AMERICAN FUEL & PETROCHEMICAL MANUFACTURERS ASSOCIATION, et al., petitioners,
v.
Richard W. COREY, in His Official Capacity as Executive Officer of the California Air Resources Board, et al. No. 13-1149. Supreme Court of the United States June 30, 2014.
